sequenceDiagram
    participant SA as Super Admin
    participant P as Principal
    participant S as Student
    participant UI as React Frontend
    participant API as Node.js API
    participant SOC as Socket.IO Server
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant A as Committee Member

    rect rgb(240, 240, 240)
    note right of SA: Phase 1: Institution Onboarding
    P->>UI: 1. Registers New College
    UI->>API: POST /register
    API->>DB: Save Institution (isVerified: false)
    SA->>API: 2. Approves Institution
    API->>DB: Update Institution (isVerified: true)
    P->>UI: 3. Logs in & Creates Committee
    UI->>API: POST /register (role: committee)
    API->>DB: Save Committee Users
    end

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
    note right of SA: Phase 2: Grievance Management
    S->>UI: 4. Submits Grievance Form
    UI->>API: POST /submitComplaint (with JWT)
    API->>API: Verify JWT & Strip User ID
    API->>API: Generate unique Tracking ID
    API->>DB: 5. Save Complaint (No User Link)
    DB-->>API: Success
    API-->>UI: Return Tracking ID
    UI-->>S: Display Success & Tracking ID
    
    A->>UI: 6. Opens Complaint Details
    UI->>SOC: Join Chat Room (Tracking ID)
    S->>UI: Opens Status Page
    UI->>SOC: Join Chat Room (Tracking ID)
    
    A->>SOC: 7. emit('sendMessage', pseudoAdminId, text)
    SOC->>DB: Save Message
    SOC-->>UI: broadcast('newMessage', text)
    UI-->>S: View Message in Real-time
    end
